A pure kill count has little meaning I think.. Wouldn't be hard to level up a second charecter and just kill it a bunch over and over.  Other statistics would be interesting though.  For example average level of the player you have killed.  And only one kill of that person counts towards the average.  How many different people you have killed.. If you just make a bunch of low levels to kill you have a bad average. If you have just killed te same person over and over you don't have many kills.
